COMMENT ON COLUMN "public"."user_like"."comment_level" IS E'评论层级类型（1=根评论，2=回复评论）\n仅当 targetType=评论时有值。';
COMMENT ON COLUMN "public"."user_like"."user_id" IS E'点赞用户 ID';
